1 (3) Contracts or subcontracts with an entity that performs abortions or promotes
2 abortion;
3 (4) Becomes or continues to be affiliated with an entity that performs abortions or
4 promotes abortions; or
5 (5) Regularly makes referrals to an entity that provides abortions or promotes
6 abortion.
